snippet.title: Johnny Depp libel trial: Amber Heard’s domestic violence “fraudulent”, court hears | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► There was more drama at the High Court as Johnny Depp’s friend accused Ms Heard of filing a "fraudulent" domestic violence claim and described the actor as a "true honest guy."

Mr Depp is suing them over an article which said he beat his ex-wife Amber Heard - something he denies.
 
► Johnny Depp: Ex-partner Winona Ryder tells High Court he was ‘never violent’
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l6hFd96rsCQ&t=1s

The flagship programme at 5pm is watched by up to a million viewers, with a later bulletin broadcast at 6.30pm and regular short news updates throughout the day. 

The Channel 5 News operation is located in a bespoke state-of-the-art newsroom based at Channel 5, linked to ITN's central technical, editorial and corporate infrastructure.
